        "description": "<p>This plugin allow you to add javascript code of Google analytics counter or Yandex metrika counter.</p>\n<p>For more information visit:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://metrica.yandex.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Yandex Metrika</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.google.com/analytics\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Google Analytics</a></p>\n",
